address2: 18 Kong Yue Road JinGuZhou Zone Xinhui District
longBusinessSummary: Jolimark Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells printers and other electronic products in the People's Republic of China. The company offers rolling and flatbed dot matrix printers, passbook printers, thermal and dot matrix POS solutions, POS terminals, projectors, and other electronic products under the Jolimark brand name. It also designs, manufactures, and sells business equipment, tax control equipment, and other electronic products on EMS/ODM/OEM basis. In addition, the company is involved in the distribution of EPSON branded SIDM printers; research and development of the inkjet print heads and Internet of Things; import and export of electronic products; and sale of medical equipment. Further, it operates as a logistics agent. The company was founded in 1986 and is headquartered in Jiangmen, the People's Republic of China. Jolimark Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Kytronics Holdings Limited.
